<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h3 class="card-title">Machine-readable formats</h3>
    <p>This term is available in the following machine-readable formats:</p>
    
    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Turtle</h5>
      <p>Access the Turtle (.ttl) representation:</p>
      
      <p><a href="/terms/{{ objName }}.ttl" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">View as Turtle</a></p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl https://oerschema.org/terms/{{ objName }}.ttl</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">JSON-LD</h5>
      <p>Access the JSON-LD representation:</p>
      
      <p><a href="/terms/{{ objName }}.jsonld" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">View as JSON-LD</a></p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl https://oerschema.org/terms/{{ objName }}.jsonld</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">RDF/XML</h5>
      <p>Access the RDF/XML (.rdf) representation:</p>
      
      <p><a href="/terms/{{ objName }}.rdf" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">View as RDF/XML</a></p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl https://oerschema.org/terms/{{ objName }}.rdf</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">N-Triples</h5>
      <p>Access the N-Triples (.nt) representation:</p>
      
      <p><a href="/terms/{{ objName }}.nt" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">View as N-Triples</a></p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl https://oerschema.org/terms/{{ objName }}.nt</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Content Negotiation</h5>
      <p>OER Schema supports <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Content_negotiation" target="_blank" class="link link-primary">HTTP content negotiation</a>. You can request different representations of this term by specifying the appropriate Accept header:</p>
      
      <h6 class="font-medium mt-4 mb-2">Examples:</h6>
      
      <p>Request Turtle format:</p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -LH "Accept: text/turtle" https://oerschema.org/{{ objName }}</code></pre>
      
      <p>Request JSON-LD format:</p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -LH "Accept: application/ld+json" https://oerschema.org/{{ objName }}</code></pre>
      
      <p>Request RDF/XML format:</p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -LH "Accept: application/rdf+xml" https://oerschema.org/{{ objName }}</code></pre>
      
      <p>Request N-Triples format:</p>
      <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -LH "Accept: application/n-triples" https://oerschema.org/{{ objName }}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="py-4">
      <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Complete Vocabulary</h5>
